claim.claim-text:
1. A pre-mixed mortar, stucco or masonry composition comprising:
70 to 80 percent sand; and
20 to 30 percent light-weight cement mix composition comprising:
either slag cement, Gypsum or a combination of slag cement and gypsum;
sodium tall oil;
sodium stearate;
sodium C14-16 Alpha Olefin;
linear alkyl benzene;
silicon dioxide.

12. A pre-mixed mortar, stucco or masonry composition comprising:
approximately 75% sand; and
approximately 25% light-weight cement mix, the light weight cement mix comprising:
35 to 90 percent slag cement by weight;
1 to 3 percent sodium tall oil by weight;
1 to 2 percent sodium stearate by weight;
1 to 2 percent sodium C14-16 Alpha Olefin by weight;
1 to 3 percent linear alkyl benzene by weight;
10 to 20 percent silicon dioxide by weight.

15. A pre-mixed mortar, stucco or masonry composition comprising:
approximately 75% sand; and
approximately 25% light-weight cement mix, the light weight cement mix comprising:
35 to 90 percent slag cement by weight;
1 to 3 percent sodium tall oil by weight;
1 to 2 percent sodium stearate by weight;
1 to 2 percent sodium C14-16 Alpha Olefin by weight;
1 to 3 percent linear alkyl benzene by weight;
10 to 20 percent silicon dioxide by weight.
